plot: Oswald Löpelmann persuades Clemens to return to the old agency. Patrick Graf, who already saw himself as a secret successor to Clemens, is very disappointed when he hears about it, especially since Clemens threatens him to take revenge for the disloyal behavior. Meanwhile, a passionate interlude is brewing between Tina and Heiko. However, when Heiko wants to go to a motel with her, Tina's initial euphoria turns into rejection.
